onEquipmentName)',182,'Radiello','Air Sampler','A passive/diffusive sampler for environmental monitoring, ambient and outdoor air monitoring, industrial hygiene, industrial air quality (IAQ), personal sampling and breathing zone assessment. ','2020-07-24 20:12:15','RA'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',107,'Rectangular Net','Net/Non-Tow','','2006-08-12 00:51:17','RN'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',61,'Remotely Operated Vehicle','Miscellaneous/Other','','2006-08-12 00:51:17','ROV'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',186,'Rock Bag','Trap/Substrate','The abundance and generic richness of a macroinvertebrate community in a river or stream is determined by counting the number of species or genera in a standardized sampling unit. Rock bags allow sampling in depths as shallow as five centimeters, and can be flattened to fit stream bed contours.','2015-10-05 11:37:33','RB'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',145,'Rock Basket','Trap/Substrate','The abundance and generic richness of a macroinvertebrate community in a river or stream is determined by counting the number of species or genera in a standardized sampling unit.  Rock baskets are used for the majority of wadeable sites. ','2006-08-12 00:51:17','RBT'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',187,'Rock-filled Cone Sampler','Trap/Substrate','The abundance and generic richness of a macroinvertebrate community in a river/stream is determined by counting the number of species or genera in a standardized sampling unit. Remote-retrievable rock-filled cone samplers allow for sampling in sites that are not wadeable. These devices are retrieved by boat using a weighted, funnel-shaped apparatus that is dropped down a line to settle over the cone. The base of the cone is fitted with Nytex mesh to prevent the loss of organisms upon retrieval. ','2015-10-05 11:38:32','RFCS'),('Sample Collection Eq