d sample unless the stream is completely mixed laterally and vertically. Thus, the analytical results cannot be used to directly compute analyte discharges.','2016-01-19 11:25:07','UCMTS'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',199,'USGS field procedure for sampling Hg-CH3','Water Sampler','Instrumentation is a Cold Vapor Atomic Fluoresence Spectrophotometer. Methylmercury (sometimes methyl mercury) is an organometallic cation with the formula [CH3Hg]+. It is the major source of organic mercury for all humans. It is a bioaccumulative environmental toxicant','2016-01-19 11:25:07','UFPSHG'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',167,'Van Dorn Bottle','Water Sampler','Samplers that obtain composite samples from several depths or pool samples from one depth and thus can be used for both horizontal and vertical sampling.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VDB'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',43,'Van Veen Grab','Benthic Grab','A grab that relies on the closure of two opposing jaws for the collection of a sediment sample. The van Veen grab has long arms attached to each bucket, thus giving better leverage during closure. This type of grab has been used widely in benthic macrofauna studies, it is not recommended for use on coarser substrata.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VVG'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',119,'Variable Mesh Gill Net','Net/Non-Tow','Gill nets are composed of vertical panels of netting that hang from a line with regularly spaced floaters that hold the line on the surface of the water.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VMGN'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',16,'Vibrating Corer','Benthic Corer','A sample corer that uses vibration to help the core penetrating the sediment.','2020-07-24 20:13:46','VCO'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',69,'Video Camera','Miscellaneous/Other','a camera for recording images on videotape or for transmitting them to a monitor screen.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VC'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',152,'Vinyl Tube','Water Sampler','Poly-vinyl Chloride (PVC) cylindrical structure or device','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VT'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',70,'Visual Sighting','Miscellaneous/Other','an instance of seeing or observation of','2006-08-12 00:51:17','VS'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',168,'Water Bottle','Water Sampler','Bottle used for sampling water.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','WB'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',156,'Water Sampler (Other)','Water Sampler','a water sampler (vertical water bottle) is used for general water sampling in lakes, channels, wells and the sea','2006-08-12 00:51:17','WSO'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',177,'WBH-96','Water Sampler','A weighted bottle sampler that is a stainless steel metal housing used to secure a bottle for sampling in streams with a velocity too low for isokinetic samplers. Usually an open mouth bottle or a bottle with a US D-77 or US D-95 cap without a nozzle is used. The metal housing has holes drilled near the top for a rope line that is used to secure the bottle and deploy the sampler. It should always be documented that a sample taken with the weighted bottle sampler is not an isokinetic sample.','2011-12-08 16:51:39','W96'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',170,'Whirl-pak bag','Water Sampler','Sterile polyethylene bags with sodium thiosulfate that are disposable, transparent bags for water sampling.','2010-04-28 09:13:42','WPB'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',125,'Wisconsin-Style Net','Net/Vertical Tow','this net enables quantitative vertical plankton hauls.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','WN'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',200,'XAD resin','Air Sampler','A type of sampling media used in air sampling, onto/into which the contaminant is collected. Resin is a hydrophobic organic porous polymer.','2016-01-19 11:25:07','XR'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',201,'XAD-2 resin','Air Sampler','A type of sampling media used in air sampling, onto/into which the contaminant is collected. Resin is a hydrophobic organic porous polymer.','2016-01-19 11:25:07','X2R'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',84,'Yankee Trawl','Net/Horizontal Tow','Two Panel Net','2006-08-12 00:51:17','YT'),('Sample Collection Equipment(SampleCollectionEquipmentName)',44,'Young Grab','Benthic Grab','The Young Grab, or the Young Modified Van Veen Grab Sampler is an instrument to sample sediment in the ocean. It is a modified version of the Van Veen grab sampler, with a clamshell bucket made out of stainless steel mounted to a supporting frame.','2006-08-12 00:51:17','YG');
